premise_source_doc_sentence: Margaret Ruth `` Margot '' Kidder  (  born October 17 , 1948  )  is a Canadian American actress and activist .
Tribulation , also known as Apocalypse III : Tribulation , is a 2000 thriller film by Cloud Ten Pictures , starring Gary Busey , Howie Mandel , Nick Mancuso , and Margot Kidder .
